gov/21858793/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Oncologic+emergencies%3A+pathophysiology%2C+presentation%2C+diagnosis%2C+and+treatment&amp;author=MA+Lewis&amp;author=AW+Hendrickson&amp;author=TJ+Moynihan&amp;publication_year=2011&amp;journal=CA+Cancer+J+Clin&amp;pages=287-314&amp;pmid=21858793">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">4.</div><div id="r4" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Ahn S, Lee YS, Lim KS, Lee JL. Emergency department cancer unit and management of oncologic emergencies: experience in Asan Medical Center. <em>Support Care Cancer</em> 2012;20(9):2205–2210.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s00520-012-1478-8">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/22555446/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Emergency+department+cancer+unit+and+management+of+oncologic+emergencies%3A+experience+in+Asan+Medical+Center&amp;author=S+Ahn&amp;author=YS+Lee&amp;author=KS+Lim&amp;author=JL+Lee&amp;publication_year=2012&amp;journal=Support+Care+Cancer&amp;pages=2205-2210&amp;doi=10.1007%2Fs00520-012-1478-8&amp;pmid=22555446">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">5.</div><div id="r5" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Higdon ML, Higdon JA. Treatment of oncologic emergencies. <em>Am Fam Physician</em> 2006;74(11): 1873–1880.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/17168344/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Treatment+of+oncologic+emergencies&amp;author=ML+Higdon&amp;author=JA+Higdon&amp;publication_year=2006&amp;journal=Am+Fam+Physician&amp;pages=1873-1880&amp;pmid=17168344">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">6.</div><div id="r6" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Quint LE. Thoracic complications and emergencies in oncologic patients. <em>Cancer Imaging</em> 2009;9(Spec No A):S75–S82.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1102/1470-7330.2009.9031">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/19965299/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Thoracic+complications+and+emergencies+in+oncologic+patients&amp;author=LE+Quint&amp;publication_year=2009&amp;journal=Cancer+Imaging&amp;pages=S75-S82&amp;doi=10.1102%2F1470-7330.2009.9031&amp;pmid=19965299">Google Scholar</a></div></div></div></div></div><div role="listitem" data-has="label"><div class="label">7.</div><div id="r7" class="citations"><div class="citation"><div class="citation-content">Katabathina VS, Restrepo CS, Martinez-Jimenez S, Riascos RF. Nonvascular, nontraumatic mediastinal emergencies in adults: a comprehensive review of imaging findings. <em>RadioGraphics</em> 2011;31(4): 1141–1160.</div><div class="external-links"><div class="core-xlink-crossref"><a href="https://doi.org/10.1148/rg.314105177">Crossref</a></div><div class="core-xlink-pubmed"><a href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/21768244/">PubMed</a></div><div class="core-xlink-google-scholar"><a href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Nonvascular%2C+nontraumatic+mediastinal+emergencies+in+adults%3A+a+comprehensive+review+of+imaging+findings&amp;author=VS+Katabathina&amp;author=CS+Restrepo&amp;author=S+Martinez-Jimenez&amp;author=RF+Riascos&amp;publication_year=2011&amp;journal=RadioGraphics&amp;pages=1141-1160&amp;doi=10.114